":2266942,"uid":15592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T18:55:46.000Z","msg":"調轉得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n細個幾鍾意食皮蛋，食粥通常都會叫皮蛋瘦肉粥，但而家唔知點解愈來愈怕皮蛋隻味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d458958ede2af075ed9fb0246a0f09aad8ddbd8","tid":2266942,"uid":310948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T18:57:06.000Z","msg":"秋葵，好似鼻涕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6d5304ffccd0980ed2ffde2766ffd0e1866aa8","tid":2266942,"uid":88099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b2248694b9e1f37f561518c753c490e3fae7a31","tid":2266942,"uid":15592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T18:55:46.000Z","msg":"調轉得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n細個幾鍾意食皮蛋，食粥通常都會叫皮蛋瘦肉粥，但而家唔知點解愈來愈怕皮蛋隻味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T18:57:20.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n但我有時病左 屋企人仲係買皮蛋瘦肉粥返黎<br />\n我講左好多次都照買 唯有食一半就掉左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c639148d05821c27bbbbf0329655764d4bd619b6","tid":2266942,"uid":41960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"343186d0977b761db50bc05aac6ee96aacdb1d23","tid":2266942,"uid":378049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T16:55:46.000Z","msg":"苦瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n茄子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n洋蔥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔單止大個左唔抗拒去食佢地<br />\n仲變到好鐘意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T18:58:18.000Z","msg":"茄子好能難食，好似食緊嘔吐物咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38d455543466f266a47a5227b85dc90f42c83dc","tid":2266942,"uid":308751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T19:00:09.000Z","msg":"我都係洋蔥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細個真係一啖都唔食<br />\n我而家間唔中都會食下<br />\n<br />\n仲有啲甜嘅菜式以前細個都唔會食<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如咕嚕肉<br />\n依家就ok 見到有會夾多幾舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a25c91f55a9e4ae6c98fd9e08ed793de0a3008","tid":2266942,"uid":197221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T19:01:07.000Z","msg":"芫荽 <br />\n碗麵面頭有都一定夾走驚浸到湯<br />\n食到浸味都唔得 頂唔順<br />\n呢一年反而開始識欣賞佢 <br />\n直頭會成日叫老母買定一束返屋企當菜食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n芫荽配拉麵 個湯底勁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30aa75a3340c0b4607bd68c10f98ac47397964e4","tid":2266942,"uid":2949,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T19:02:59.000Z","msg":"苦瓜真係呢世都唔會鍾意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好講咩人生道理 難食就係難食"},{"pid":"1578a2229519eea540a697cd5cb3e1c75b48519e","tid":2266942,"uid":41846,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T19:33:59.000Z","msg":"蔥 芫茜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1283769f45c57a9e319d798735ca01c633c69214","tid":2266942,"uid":1660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T20:03:19.000Z","msg":"菜<br />\n細個唔鍾意食菜大個不停食<br />\n麵包餅乾 細個唔鍾意食d乾爭爭既野<br />\n大個反而食唔停<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9de14d6c24a53601417017b731face92a60ed19","tid":2266942,"uid":345286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T20:19:16.000Z","msg":"洋蔥、蒽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004ba